nl_querry: User No.23853 gave a comment to a post at 9:08:18 on 2013/7/12, was that post well-finished? user no. 23853 refers to UserId = '23853'; at 9:08:18 on 2013/7/12 refers to CreationDate = '2013-07-12 09:08:18.0'; not well-finished refers to ClosedDate IS NULL and vice versa
llm_querry: SELECT CASE WHEN T2.ClosedDate IS NOT NULL THEN 'Yes' ELSE 'No' END AS IsWellFinished FROM comments AS T1 INNER JOIN posts AS T2 ON T1.PostId = T2.Id WHERE T1.UserId = 23853 AND T1.CreationDate = '2013-07-12 09:08:18.0'
gold_querry: SELECT IF(T2.ClosedDate IS NULL, 'NOT well-finished', 'well-finished') AS resylt FROM comments AS T1 INNER JOIN posts AS T2 ON T1.PostId = T2.Id WHERE T1.UserId = 23853 AND T1.CreationDate = '2013-07-12 09:08:18.0'
